estate decision for you.<\/p><p>There\u2019s no question that buying or selling a home is more than a financial undertaking; it\u2019s also an emotional and life changing event. At times it can seem overwhelming, but it doesn\u2019t have to be. Let me show you just how fun it can be to find your dream home when you\u2019re working with a professional that truly cares about you and your family.<\/p><p>REALTOR\u00ae<br \/>Top Producer 2013 and 2014<br \/>Five Star Award Winner 2016<br \/>Certified Negotiations Expert (CNE)<br \/>Accredited Buyer\u2019s Representative (ABR) designation<br \/>Certified Luxury Home Marketing Specialist (CLHMS) designation<br \/>Graduate of Realtor Institute (GRI) designation<br \/>Specialty Buyer\u2019s Representative in New Home Sales<br \/>Member of the Austin Board of Realtors<br \/>Member of the Texas Association of Realtors<br \/>Member of the National Association of Realtors<br \/>BS in Communication Studies from the University of Texas at Austin<\/p><p><strong>Office:<\/strong> 512.342.1800\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac11626 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"ac11626\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<style>\n.elementor-column.elementor-col-33 ul.elementor-icon-list-items {\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n}    \n<\/style>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Management Team Miquele Dunkley Sales Director Contact Born and raised in Austin, I have developed a true love and passion for this city and its people. My husband also grew up in Austin and the two of us cannot imagine a greater place to build a life together with our three children. I have been [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"auth